# UHF RFID reader driver (J4210U / 910 / 903) configuration

config UHF_UART_TXD_PIN
    int "UART TX GPIO pin (connected to reader RX)"
    default 17
    help
        GPIO number for UART TX. Connect this to the UHF reader's RX pin.

config UHF_UART_RXD_PIN
    int "UART RX GPIO pin (connected to reader TX)"
    default 16
    help
        GPIO number for UART RX. Connect this to the UHF reader's TX pin.
